===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|yeerly}}, {{m|enm|yerely}}, from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{m|ang|ġēarlīc||yearly, of the year, annual}}, equivalent to {{suffix|year|ly|lang=en}}. Cognate with {{etyl|sco|-}} {{m|sco|yerelie||yearly}}, {{etyl|stq|-}} {{m|stq|jierelk||yearly}}, {{etyl|fy|-}} {{m|fy|jierliks||yearly}}, {{etyl|nl|-}} {{m|nl|jaarlijks||yearly}}, {{etyl|de|-}} {{m|de|jährlich||yearly}}, {{etyl|sv|-}} {{m|sv|årlig||yearly}}, {{etyl|is|-}} {{m|is|árlegur||yearly}}.

